name: Kamar Gelap
description:
“Kamar gelap” in a room without light, is it still necessary to look outside? wouldnt it stay the same in the dark. without needing to reveal what happened, we can swing ourselves, hold on, live and absorb all the available energy or we blow our minds by redistributing bodily functions, or back to ourselves it all depends on each of us to question whatever is there. life is just a matter of delaying death
.
Chose to create an archive about what happened in 2020 when the covid 19 pandemic hit about what I felt at that time by making this mini zine page
